duardo Jansen was a member of the gnomish Jansen, active in the late 14 century DR.
Eduardo was known for his intentions. One of his inventions was proudly displayed in Athkatlas Center District, at the center of Waukeens Promenade. Eduardos flying machine was a small device with four wings, big enough to accommodate one person. The winged machine was displayed next to another gnomish flying machine â€“ a boat attached to a big balloon.
